    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a joke. how are you supposed to rebuild when the shame is constant? every time i close my eyes i just see my dad's face when he finds out. i can't face that. i can't face the next forty years of everyone looking at me like i'm some kind of joke. there's just no way to undo the damage i've done. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just... stop.",
